metadata.name: En 37
metadata.description:
It has been encrypted, extremely small but mysterious existence.
It is a high-dimensional space body, and its projection is a three-dimensional environment surrounded by the creation of digital artist called Sun Zhongyuan. People can explore it in the metaverse in the future.
Human beings understand the world through physical research, we call this serie of work "En", the decrypting code is in the theory of physics.
